<a name="pegasus_feather_cloak"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Pegasus Feather Cloak - AC 6</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Slot: <a href="/armour/shoulders.shtml">Shoulders</a><BR>
Weight: 5.0 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/bard/armour/shoulders.shtml">BRD</a>, <a href="/cleric/armour/shoulders.shtml">CLR</a>, <a href="/druid/armour/shoulders.shtml">DRU</a>, <a href="/enchanter/armour/shoulders.shtml">ENC</a>, <a href="/magician/armour/shoulders.shtml">MAG</a>, <a href="/monk/armour/shoulders.shtml">MNK</a>, <a href="/necromancer/armour/shoulders.shtml">NEC</a>, <a href="/paladin/armour/shoulders.shtml">PAL</a>, <a href="/ranger/armour/shoulders.shtml">RNG</a>, <a href="/rogue/armour/shoulders.shtml">ROG</a>, <a href="/shadow_knight/armour/shoulders.shtml">SHD</a>, <a href="/shaman/armour/shoulders.shtml">SHM</a>, <a href="/warrior/armour/shoulders.shtml">WAR</a>, <a href="/wizard/armour/shoulders.shtml">WIZ</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/levitate.shtml?spellID=557">Levitate</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) <BR>
(DEX +7) </font>
<BR>
Dropped in South Karana by Quillmane.<BR>

