<td width=50%><font color=white>Posted By: Gavilan</font></td><td width=50% align=right><font color=white>2000-05-08 06:39:24</font></td></tr><tr>
<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I Just got the cloak. I was so lucky to run into her on my way to kill shadowed me for the shadowed rapier to get my Jboots. I quickly set upon her with a couple of Nukes and then I see a druid and a ranger try to Kill steal from me. Luckily I am lvl 41 and my Nukes did more damage. Here is what I have found:<BR>
The cloak is a shoulder item but can be kept in an open inventory slot for the effect. As long as you stand still you can recast Levitation before it runs out. <BR>
I knew it was a rare spawn but did not know the cloak was a rare drop.<BR>
<BR>
<BR>
Good luck on getting your cloak!<BR>
