<td colspan=2 bgcolor="#0000AF"><font color=white>I have seen quillmane spawn 3 times now. On the first 2 times ppl from everywhere came in to kill it. Never mind the group there taking her down... When she spawns no one is worried about being called a KS'er.. Sad..<BR>
<BR>
3rd time she spawn i ran her away from all who would try KS.. Irony is other 2 times she dropped the pants.. My group got the Cloak.. Lovely bit of kit.. No more swiming..<BR>
<BR>
I have seen her all 3 times at the sth spire outside paw.. Even con to a 30th character.. She was heading from the direction of aviak city to the back of the spires.. If you try kill her at the spires beware of everyone jumping in trying to get the kill..<BR>
<BR>
As most ppl have said before:<BR>
<BR>
1. Cloak worn on the shoulder slot.<BR>
2. Can be in an inv slot to cast levitate.<BR>
3. Can recast levitate as long as you are stationary.<BR>
4. Levitate can only be cast on holder of cloak.<BR>
5. Quillmane is not a 12 hour spawn. Seen her spawn after 2 hours of being killed.<BR>
6. Lvl 30 critter.</font></td></tr></table>
